{"tid":640912,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"真正嘅三文魚係唔會食日本人","createTime":"2018-04-24T15:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T21:10:56.000Z","uid":28938,"like":22,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bd023d30bd5eae8b72d9c26a52f1e44719cd4323","tid":640912,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身，因為三文魚們老早知道人肉的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活人，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的人都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n日本人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的日本人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？"},{"pid":"911d68ad3f6d9542b7cb50a0ebfb01a02b29275a","tid":640912,"uid":167882,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"1分"},{"pid":"46979b1d39610080d6aebc26e66881fab60cbb50","tid":640912,"uid":91982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6001422c0314db3a94588c89f7fa6523bf04bdec","tid":640912,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7bd66c334a7bca5739e276be89598dde8967b6","tid":640912,"uid":150848,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:45:28.000Z","msg":"其他三文魚會食人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044f2730a5791b87b9d4cac33990260751cd227f","tid":640912,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca30f8c6890e3f80aef6c85d2fb660efb144c6d0","tid":640912,"uid":87338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:29:43.000Z","msg":"好好笑啊 哈哈哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n